description: Sansui - 34" Curved WQHD 165Hz Gaming Monitor - Black
notes: Immerse yourself in vivid detail with the Sansui G34 Series 34 In. Curved Fast VA LED Monitor, engineered for professional performance and cinematic immersion. The Fast VA panel ensures deep contrast (3000:1) and vivid color accuracy, covering 97 % DCI-P3 and 130 % sRGB, ideal for content creators and visual enthusiasts. HDR support adds dynamic brightness and depth, while Adaptive Sync technology eliminates tearing for a smooth, stutter-free experience. Designed for comfort, this monitor includes Low Blue Light and Anti-Flicker Eye-Care Technology, reducing strain during long sessions. Its metal stand offers -5° to 15° tilt adjustability and premium durability, with VESA 75 × 75 mm compatibility for flexible mounting. Connectivity is seamless through HDMI 2.1 and DisplayPort 1.4, supporting up to 165 Hz refresh rates on modern PCs and consoles. The built-in PIP/PBP mode allows multitasking across two devices simultaneously. Stylish, high-performance, and versatile, the Sansui G34 redefines ultrawide productivity and entertainment—perfect for those who demand stunning visuals and exceptional smoothness in every frame.

description: (6 PACK) Adhesive Magnetic Cable Clips - Cable Management Clips for Charging Cables
notes:
【Magnetic Design】The magnetic cable clip uses a sophisticated 90° rotating shaft and magnetic locking cord design that prevents the power cable from falling off. It enables one-handed placement and removal of cables and firmly secures the power cable in place.
【No Residual Acrylic Adhesive】Upgraded acrylic adhesive pads allow the cable organizer to stick firmly to almost any flat, clean smooth surfaces, such as tiles, steel, glass, wood, etc. It will not damage your desktop or wall and leave no residue.
【Easy to Install】In just three steps, you can place the magnet organizer anywhere you want to use it: 1. Clean the surface. 2. Paste the acrylic tape. 3. Press evenly and clamp the wire.
【Wide Compatibility】The cable organizer can hold cables in place firmly with a diameter of 0.27 inches (7mm), it can hold most cables, such as phone charging cables, USB cables, Nylon Braided Cables, computer power wireless, etc.
【Multiple Scenarios for Use】The 6-pack set is versatile for organizing cords in different scenarios, such as on an office desk, kitchen table edge, table corner, wall, or car dashboard. The cord holder, measuring 0.78 inches, can be securely fixed in narrow spaces. It doesn't take up much room and can be hidden in any small corner.
